    alt Input passes safety checks
        Orch->>GenServer: Generate text<br/>gRPC (fmaas.GenerationService), TLS/mTLS
        GenServer-->>Orch: Generated text
        Orch->>OutputDet: Detect output content safety<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS/mTLS (configurable)
        OutputDet-->>Orch: Output detection results
    end
    Orch-->>Client: GuardrailsTextGenerationResponse<br/>with detections
    Orch--)OTEL: Traces & Metrics (OTLP)

    Note over Client,OutputDet: Flow 2: Chat Completions with Detection
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>TLS (optional), mTLS (optional)
    Orch->>InputDet: Detect chat input safety<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS/mTLS
    InputDet-->>Orch: Input detection results
    alt Input passes safety checks
